不公<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1287617\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1287617</a><br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n團結内部勢力<br />\n10.請參考<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1285088/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1285088/page/2</a><br />\n詳細方法見#20"},{"pid":"abdff8f9f30852944dedbb5f743922005f9bef8d","tid":1289700,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T09:13:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fe68165a13f183fbcfec862dca849dc71ea25a89","tid":1289700,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T09:13:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fd51b6d2ae3a87e299442518c0d7f71e4eac1ca4","tid":1289700,"uid":38030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T09:13:59.000Z","msg":"上次條藍絲撐犬化妝師就係做am730，自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca32b522dde768121fa9823c69b49a0930ffb565","tid":1289700,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T09:14:17.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n千萬不能閉門會議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14cd9318723f90902e68626e8e7b46ca6dc4c9d9","tid":1289700,"uid":17741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T09:14:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b85854f7a26db